'''佩什梅格'''（[[索拉尼库尔德语|库尔德语]]：{{lang|ckb|{{big|پێشمەرگە}}}} ''{{lang|ku|Pêşmerge}}''，意为“面对死亡的人”）是[[伊拉克库尔德斯坦|伊拉克库尔德斯坦]]自治区的[[武装力量|武装力量]]<ref>来自[[库尔德语|库尔德语]] ''{{lang|ku|pêş}}'' ({{lang|ckb|{{big|پێش}}}}) “面对”和 ''{{lang|ku|merg}}'' {{lang|ckb|{{big|مەرگ}}}}“死亡”。</ref>。佩什梅格的正式领导者是[[伊拉克库尔德斯坦总统|伊拉克库尔德斯坦总统]]。这支武装力量本身在很大程度上被划分为两部分，分别由[[库尔德斯坦民主党|库尔德斯坦民主党]]和[[库尔德斯坦爱国联盟|库尔德斯坦爱国联盟]]领导，虽然这两个政党都宣誓效忠[[库尔德斯坦地区政府|库尔德斯坦地区政府]]。目前，相关部门正在协调以期将整个部队集结于佩什梅格事务部的领导下。<ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite web |first=Mahmoud |last=Nawzad |title=Sources: Barzani Orders Peshmerga Forces Reformed, United |url=http://rudaw.net/english/kurdistan/250820142 |work=[[Rudaw_Media_Network|Rudaw Media Network]] |date=25 August 2014 |accessdate=13 February 2015 |archive-date=2016-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108134240/http://rudaw.net/english/kurdistan/250820142 |dead-url=no }}</ref>佩什梅格部队的职责是保卫库尔德地区的国土、人民和自治政府。<ref>{{cite web |title=Summary of the most important tasks of the Ministry of Peshmerga |url=http://mope.krg.org/about-e.php?z=8&l=3 |work=Ministry of Peshmerga |date=12 November 2012 |accessdate=13 February 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112042513/http://mope.krg.org/about-e.php?z=8&l=3 |archivedate=2015年1月12日 }}</ref>

因为[[伊拉克宪法|伊拉克宪法]]規定[[伊拉克陆军|伊拉克陆军]]不得进入[[伊拉克库尔德斯坦|伊拉克库尔德斯坦]]，<ref>{{cite web |title=Iraqi PM criticizes Kurdish region for barring army from Syrian border area |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2012-07/28/c_131745233.htm |work=[[Xinhua_News_Agency|Xinhua News Agency]] |date=28 July 2012 |accessdate=13 February 2015 |archive-date=2016-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160606223640/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/world/2012-07/28/c_131745233.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Information about Kurdistan |url=http://heevie.org/aboutkurdistan |work=Kurdistan Development Organization |date=2014 |accessdate=13 February 2015 |archive-date=2020-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053034/http://heevie.org/aboutkurdistan |dead-url=no }}</ref>所以佩什梅格以及其它的库尔德安全附属机构负责库尔德地区的安全事务。<ref>{{cite web |first=Jay |last=Newton-Small |title=Destination Kurdistan: Is This Autonomous Iraqi Region a Budding Tourist Hot Spot? |url=http://world.time.com/2012/12/31/destination-kurdistan-is-this-autonomous-iraqi-region-a-budding-tourist-hotspot/ |work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] |date=31 December 2012 |accessdate=13 February 2015 |archive-date=2019-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816214014/http://world.time.com/2012/12/31/destination-kurdistan-is-this-autonomous-iraqi-region-a-budding-tourist-hotspot/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Heath |last=Druzin |title=Rare terrorist attack in peaceful Kurdish region of Iraq kills 6 |url=http://www.stripes.com/news/middle-east/rare-terrorist-attack-in-peaceful-kurdish-region-of-iraq-kills-6-1.244095 |work=[[Stars_and_Stripes_(newspaper)|Stars and Stripes]] |date=29 September 2013 |accessdate=13 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117021841/http://www.stripes.com/news/middle-east/rare-terrorist-attack-in-peaceful-kurdish-region-of-iraq-kills-6-1.244095 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Jenna |last=Krajeski |title=The Iraq War Was a Good Idea, If You Ask the Kurds |url=http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2013/03/the-iraq-war-was-a-good-idea-if-you-ask-the-kurds/274196/ |work=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]] |date=20 March 2013 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117030728/http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2013/03/the-iraq-war-was-a-good-idea-if-you-ask-the-kurds/274196/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>这些附属机构包括Asayish（官方情报机构）、''Parastin u Zanyarî''（协助情报机构）和Zeravani（宪兵队）。

在2003年[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]期间，据说佩什梅格在抓捕[[萨达姆·侯赛因|萨达姆·侯赛因]]的任务中发挥了关键作用。<ref>{{cite web |first=Manish |last=Rai |title=Kurdish Peshmerga Can Be A Game Changer In Iraq And Syria |url=http://www.khaama.com/kurdish-peshmerga-can-be-a-game-changer-in-iraq-and-syria-6802 |work=[[Khaama_Press|Khaama Press]] |date=6 October 2014 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |archive-date=2016-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108134241/http://www.khaama.com/kurdish-peshmerga-can-be-a-game-changer-in-iraq-and-syria-6802 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Operation Red Dawn's eight-month hunt |url=http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2003/12/15/1071336860245.html |work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]] |date=15 December 2003 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151214101803/http://www.smh.com.au/articles/2003/12/15/1071336860245.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2004年，库尔德反恐怖主义力量抓获了[[基地组织|基地组织]]核心人物[[哈桑·古尔|哈桑·古尔]]，哈桑·古尔透露了[[本·拉登|本·拉登]]信使的身份，最终导致[[奥萨马·本·拉登之死|本·拉登的死亡]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://theweek.com/article/index/243389/how-the-cia-really-caught-bin-ladens-trail#axzz34IzUbxqb |last=Ambinder |first=Marc |title=How the CIA really caught Bin Laden's trail |newspaper=[[The_Week|The Week]] |date=29 April 2013 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111123347/https://theweek.com/article/index/243389/how-the-cia-really-caught-bin-ladens-trail#axzz34IzUbxqb |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Arom |last=Roston |title=Cloak and Drone: The Strange Saga of an Al Qaeda Triple Agent |url=http://www.vocativ.com/usa/nat-sec/cloak-drone-strange-saga-al-qaeda-triple-agent/ |work=[[Vocativ|Vocativ]] |date=9 January 2014 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |archive-date=2019-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190625232507/https://www.vocativ.com/usa/nat-sec/cloak-drone-strange-saga-al-qaeda-triple-agent/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在2014年8月[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]对伊拉克库尔德斯坦发动大规模[[2014年8月伊拉克北部攻势|进攻]]后，佩什梅格和来自邻国的其他库尔德武装力量在伊拉克和叙利亚发动了针对ISIS的战争。

==历史==
[[File:Barzani1.jpg|110px]]
库尔德渴望独立的尚武传统已存在了几千年，早期的库尔德战士抗击各个波斯帝国、奥斯曼帝国和大英帝国。<ref name="main history source">{{cite web |first=Michael G. |last=Lortz |title=Willing to Face Death: A History of Kurdish Military Forces – the ''Peshmerga'' – from the Ottoman Empire to Present-Day Iraq |url=http://diginole.lib.fsu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=3203&context=etd |format=PDF |work=MA Thesis |publisher=[[Florida_State_University|Florida State University]] |date=28 October 2005 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150727174333/http://diginole.lib.fsu.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=3203&context=etd |archivedate=2015年7月27日 }}</ref>而“佩什梅格”这个词是由已故的库尔德作家[[易卜拉欣·艾哈迈德|易卜拉欣·艾哈迈德]]于二十世纪中叶创造的。<ref>{{cite web |first=Allegra |last=Stratton |title=Hero of the people |url=http://www.newstatesman.com/node/153517 |work=[[New_Statesman|New Statesman]] |date=26 June 2006 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929141306/https://www.newstatesman.com/node/153517 |dead-url=no }}</ref>历史上，“佩什梅格”只是作为游击队组织存在，但是在自行宣称的[[马哈巴德共和国|马哈巴德共和国]]（1946年–1947年）时期，“佩什梅格”成为了由[[穆斯塔法·巴尔扎尼|穆斯塔法·巴尔扎尼]]领导的国家军队。<ref name="first mahabad source">{{cite web |first=Mufid |last=Abdulla |title=Mahabad – the first independent Kurdish republic |url=http://kurdistantribune.com/2011/mahabad-first-independent-kurdish-republic/ |work=The Kurdistan Tribune |date=12 June 2011 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |archive-date=2016-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160528231328/http://kurdistantribune.com/2011/mahabad-first-independent-kurdish-republic/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ma barzani"/>在共和国垮台以及国家元首[[卡齐·穆罕默德|卡齐·穆罕默德]]被处决后，“佩什梅格”重新分裂成为若干游击队组织，在20世纪余下时期里继续对抗着[[伊朗|伊朗]]和[[伊拉克政府|伊拉克政府]]。<ref>{{cite book |first=Susan |last=Meiselas |title=Kurdistan: In the Shadow of History |edition=2nd |publisher=[[University_of_Chicago_Press|University of Chicago Press]] |date=2008 |isbn=978-0-226-51928-9}}</ref>

在伊拉克，大部分的“佩什梅格”士兵由[[库尔德民主党|库尔德民主党]]的[[穆斯塔法·巴尔扎尼|穆斯塔法·巴尔扎尼]]领导。<ref name="ma barzani">{{cite web |title=President |url=http://www.krgspain.org/government/profiles/english-president/ |work=[[Kurdistan_Regional_Government|Kurdistan Regional Government Representation in Spain]] |date=2015 |accessdate=14 February 2015 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925140538/http://www.krgspain.org/government/profiles/english-president/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>1975年，“佩什梅格”在[[第二次伊库战争|第二次伊库战争]]中战败。同年，库尔德民主党的高层人物[[贾拉勒·塔拉巴尼|贾拉勒·塔拉巴尼]]排除阻力建立了[[库尔德斯坦爱国联盟|库尔德斯坦爱国联盟]]。这次事件引起了库尔德民主党的不满，两派的冲突也造成了“佩什梅格”和库尔德社会的分隔。

穆斯塔法·巴尔扎尼死后，他的儿子马苏德·巴尔扎尼继承了他的领导职位。<ref name="ma barzani" />随着库尔德民主党和库尔德斯坦爱国联盟的矛盾加剧，大部分的“佩什梅格”既要保卫各自政党控制的领地又要对抗伊拉克军队的入侵。在[[两伊战争|两伊战争]]时期，伊拉克库尔德斯坦陷入了两大库尔德政党之间的[[伊拉克库尔德斯坦内战|内战]]状态下，各自领导的“佩什梅格”部队被用来打击对方。当巴尔扎尼和塔拉巴尼签署了和平条约后，内战于1998年9月正式结束。<ref>{{cite web |first=Frman |last=Abdulrahman |title=never ending mystery: what really happened to kurdish civil war missing |url=http://www.niqash.org/articles/?id=3000 |work=niqash |date=23 February 2012 |accessdate=22 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119074153/http://www.niqash.org/articles/?id=3000 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在该协议中，双方同意分享财政收入和权力，拒绝将伊拉克北部交给[[土耳其库尔德工人党|土耳其库尔德工人党]]使用，也不允许伊拉克部队进入库尔德地区。双方共有约5000名库尔德人在內戰中被殺，而更多的人则是被驱逐到了对方的领地里。<ref>{{cite web |first=Charles |last=McDermid |title=New force emerges in Kirkuk |url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Middle_East/LB20Ak02.html |work=[[Asia_Times_Online|Asia Times Online]] |date=20 February 2010 |accessdate=22 February 2015 |archive-date=2018-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180317071215/http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Middle_East/LB20Ak02.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>多年后，气氛仍高度紧张，但双方走向对方，在2003年，两党都参与了作为[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克战争]]一部分的[[推翻萨达姆政权|推翻萨达姆政权]]的战斗中。他们保持着和平的状态，形成了现在的伊拉克库尔德斯坦。不像其他的民兵部队，佩什梅格从来没有受到伊拉克法律的禁止。<ref name=WhoPeshmerga>[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28738975 Profile: Who are the Peshmerga?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-28738975 |date=20170910080051 }} BBC News. Retrieved 19 December 2014.</ref>

2015年，佩什梅格士兵第一次接受了由外国教练——[[坚决行动联合特遣队|坚决行动联合特遣队]]传授的城市作战和军事情报的训练。<ref>{{cite news|title=EXCLUSIVE: Coalition helps Peshmerga muscle up on urban warfare|url=http://rudaw.net/english/kurdistan/160420155|accessdate=17 April 2015|work=Rudaw|date=16 April 2015|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001120914/http://rudaw.net/english/kurdistan/160420155|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==构成==
