佩什梅格武装力量的确切规模未知，估计的人数从80000人到250000人不等。<ref>{{cite web |first=Peter |last=Beaumont |title=How effective is Isis compared with the Iraqi army and Kurdish peshmerga? |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/12/how-battle-ready-isis-iraqi-army-peshmerga |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=12 June 2014 |accessdate=22 February 2015 |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211120607/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/12/how-battle-ready-isis-iraqi-army-peshmerga |dead-url=no }}</ref>这些部队被分成36个[[旅|旅]]，分别被库尔德民主党、库尔德斯坦爱国联盟和佩什梅格事务部控制，且几乎没有相互协调。<ref>{{cite web |first=Fazel |last=Hawramy |title=THE DESASTROUS COMMAND-NON-COMMAND-STRUCTURE |url=http://www.mesop.de/mesop-the-desastrous-command-non-command-structure/ |work=MESOP |date=14 January 2015 |accessdate=22 February 2015 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210083717/http://www.mesop.de/mesop-the-desastrous-command-non-command-structure/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

佩什梅格武装力量正如伊拉克库尔德斯坦一样，充斥着腐败、党派偏见、裙带关系和欺诈。<ref>{{cite web |first1=Joe |last1=Parkinson |first2=Dion |last2=Nissenbaum |title=U.S., Allies Training Kurds on Using Sophisticated Weaponry Against Islamic State |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-allies-training-kurds-on-using-sophisticated-weaponry-against-islamic-state-1411339625 |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |subscription=yes |date=2015 |accessdate=22 February 2015 |archive-date=2020-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021025739/https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-allies-training-kurds-on-using-sophisticated-weaponry-against-islamic-state-1411339625 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Peshmerga of Iraq |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/programmes/insideiraq/2008/03/2008525185811788617.html |work=[[Aljazeera.com|Aljazeera.com]] |date=1 March 2008 |accessdate=22 February 2015 |archive-date=2020-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053205/https://www.aljazeera.com/programmes/insideiraq/2008/03/2008525185811788617.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |script-title=en:KRG and the ‘godfathers': 2006 secret US cable on Wikileaks |url=http://kurdistantribune.com/2014/krg-godfathers-2006-secret-cable-on-wikileaks/ |work=The Kurdistan Tribune |date=8 May 2014 |accessdate=22 February 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211749/http://kurdistantribune.com/2014/krg-godfathers-2006-secret-cable-on-wikileaks/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Jacqueline |last=Devigne |title="Iraqoncilable" Differences? The Political Nature of the Peshmerga |url=http://tiglarchives.org/sites/default/files/resources/nimep/v5/NIMEP_Insights_2011_48-64.pdf |format=PDF |work=NIMEP Insights |date=2011 |accessdate=22 February 2015 |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001192611/http://tiglarchives.org/sites/default/files/resources/nimep/v5/NIMEP_Insights_2011_48-64.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theiqdteamconnection.com/iraq-news/presidency-of-the-province-renews-its-call-to-convert-the-peshmerga-army-national|title=Presidency of the province renews its call to convert the Peshmerga Army National|work=The I.Q.D. Team Connection|accessdate=20 March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113043937/http://www.theiqdteamconnection.com/iraq-news/presidency-of-the-province-renews-its-call-to-convert-the-peshmerga-army-national|archivedate=2015年1月13日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ekurd.net/mismas/articles/misc2014/3/state7820.htm|title=PUK official warns Peshmerga will not take orders from anyone else: Iraqi Kurdistan|publisher=|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053225/https://ekurd.net/mismas/articles/misc2014/3/state7820.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>库尔德民主党带领的佩什梅格部队负责[[杜胡克省|杜胡克省]]和[[埃尔比勒省|埃尔比勒省]]的安保工作，而库尔德斯坦爱国联盟带领的佩什梅格部队负责[[苏莱曼尼亚省|苏莱曼尼亚省]]的安保工作。<ref>Chapman, Dennis. Security Forces of Kurdistan Regional Government, Us Army War College. 2009, page. 3.</ref>2014年6月[[伊斯蘭國|ISIS]]入侵伊拉克，伊拉克军队撤退后，库尔德地区政府（KRG）填补了空白并控制了几乎所有有争议的地区。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://reliefweb.int/report/iraq/jihadist-drive-allows-iraq-kurds-take-disputed-areas|title=Jihadist drive allows Iraq Kurds to take disputed areas|work=ReliefWeb|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2016-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718122723/http://reliefweb.int/report/iraq/jihadist-drive-allows-iraq-kurds-take-disputed-areas|dead-url=no}}</ref>这些地区后来也被划分为两党佩什梅格各自的控制区。

由于没有一个统一的指挥部可以统领全军，佩什梅格各部只能依靠政治上的忠诚而追随各自的领导团体。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://lebanonwire.com/1409MLN/14091314STR.asp |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113050615/http://lebanonwire.com/1409MLN/14091314STR.asp |archivedate=2015-01-13 }}</ref>不过，佩什梅格的领导团体一直在试图减少党派偏见，禁止在战场上使用党派旗帜。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.shafaaq.com/index.php/politics/10849-barzani-prevents-lifting-partisan-flags-in-fighting-fronts-except-for-kurdistan-flag|title=Barzani prevents lifting partisan flags in fighting fronts except for Kurdistan flag|publisher=|accessdate=20 March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112051404/http://english.shafaaq.com/index.php/politics/10849-barzani-prevents-lifting-partisan-flags-in-fighting-fronts-except-for-kurdistan-flag|archivedate=2015年1月12日}}</ref>一项将整个部队统一到地区政府单一指挥的政治改革也正在进行中。<ref name="ReferenceA"/>截止到2015年1月，36个旅中已有12个纳入库尔德地区政府的控制之下，剩余70%的兵力依然由两党把控。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2015/01/iraq-kurdish-peshmerga-division-islamic-state.html#|title=Kurdish peshmerga divisions hamper war effort - Al-Monitor: the Pulse of the Middle East|work=Al-Monitor|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150922034757/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2015/01/iraq-kurdish-peshmerga-division-islamic-state.html|archive-date=2015-09-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

由于资金有限而军队规模庞大，库尔德民主党一直计划将军事素质较低而人员众多的部队缩减成规模更小但效率更高且训练有素的部队。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.dk/books?id=S6oP3Y9ZM3sC&pg=PA129&lpg=PA129&dq=15%27th+and+16%27th+division+peshmerga&source=bl&ots=c0IHY4AnSX&sig=UWDppeBU7nS4a3Lqe9dMc_7Aekk&hl=da&sa=X&ei=uxWzVMWRCurNygOq94CABw&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=15'th%20and%2016'th%20division%20peshmerga&f=false|title=Withdrawal from Iraq|publisher=|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053250/https://books.google.dk/books?id=S6oP3Y9ZM3sC&pg=PA129&lpg=PA129&dq=15%27th+and+16%27th+division+peshmerga&source=bl&ots=c0IHY4AnSX&sig=UWDppeBU7nS4a3Lqe9dMc_7Aekk&hl=da&sa=X&ei=uxWzVMWRCurNygOq94CABw&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=15'th%20and%2016'th%20division%20peshmerga&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ekurd.net/mismas/articles/misc2011/1/state4537.htm|title=Iraqi Kurdistan Armed Forces, Peshmerga, to Lose 130,000 Soldiers|publisher=|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053255/https://ekurd.net/mismas/articles/misc2011/1/state4537.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 因此，在2009年，库尔德民主党和巴格达商议将部分佩什梅格士兵并入[[伊拉克陆军|伊拉克陆军]]，成立第15和第16师。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.dk/books?id=KgEo2q76J_0C&pg=PA309&lpg=PA309&dq=Peshmerga%09Projected+Residual+Force&source=bl&ots=MPM_oAI2pT&sig=wccwwoaiVcyLp3PkIhEi-WHmMvE&hl=da&sa=X&ei=MRKzVLrTIIjjywPA9IKQCg&ved=0CCQQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Peshmerga%09Projected%20Residual%20Force&f=false|title=Iraq and the United States|publisher=|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053258/https://books.google.dk/books?id=KgEo2q76J_0C&pg=PA309&lpg=PA309&dq=Peshmerga%09Projected+Residual+Force&source=bl&ots=MPM_oAI2pT&sig=wccwwoaiVcyLp3PkIhEi-WHmMvE&hl=da&sa=X&ei=MRKzVLrTIIjjywPA9IKQCg&ved=0CCQQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Peshmerga%09Projected%20Residual%20Force&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Chapman, Dennis. Security Forces of Kurdistan Regional Government, Us Army War College. 2009, page. 112.</ref>然而，埃尔比勒和巴格达之间由于争议地区关系持续紧张，转移计划被搁置。据报道，一些已经被转移的佩什梅格士兵被再次抛弃，有指控说，前佩什梅格士兵保持了对库尔德民主党的忠诚而不效忠于伊拉克军队指挥系统。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/1000-kurdish-soldiers-desert-from-iraqi-army.aspx?pageID=238&nID=48701&|title=1,000 Kurdish soldiers desert from Iraqi army - MIDEAST|publisher=|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010055820/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/1000-kurdish-soldiers-desert-from-iraqi-army.aspx?pageID=238&nID=48701&|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.dk/books?id=LzFaaWCuhdQC&pg=PA425&lpg=PA425&dq=peshmerga+iraqi+army+allegations&source=bl&ots=fDbx1jl-Oi&sig=rsdbbgjg7wAZJC29g9GMcViKk6o&hl=da&sa=X&ei=1RyzVLidL8n_ywO6-YHIBg&ved=0CD8Q6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=peshmerga%20iraqi%20army%20allegations&f=false|title=Iraq's Insurgency and the Road to Civil Conflict|publisher=|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053307/https://books.google.dk/books?id=LzFaaWCuhdQC&pg=PA425&lpg=PA425&dq=peshmerga+iraqi+army+allegations&source=bl&ots=fDbx1jl-Oi&sig=rsdbbgjg7wAZJC29g9GMcViKk6o&hl=da&sa=X&ei=1RyzVLidL8n_ywO6-YHIBg&ved=0CD8Q6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=peshmerga%20iraqi%20army%20allegations&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>
