由于库尔德地区并非独立的国家，所以佩什梅格的军火库是有限的。库尔德斯坦地方政府和伊拉克政府之间一直存在纠纷，巴格达担心库尔德人的独立倾向，便不再向伊拉克库尔德斯坦地区输送武器。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2015/01/03/iraq-peshmerga-desperate-for-us-arms-in-fight-against-isis/|title=Iraq's Peshmerga desperate for US arms in fight against ISIS|author=Hollie McKay|work=Fox News|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924190810/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2015/01/03/iraq-peshmerga-desperate-for-us-arms-in-fight-against-isis/|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dw.de/arms-for-kurdish-peshmerga-to-affect-military-balance/a-17853077|title=Arms for Kurdish peshmerga to affect military balance|work=DW.DE|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407030409/http://www.dw.de/arms-for-kurdish-peshmerga-to-affect-military-balance/a-17853077|dead-url=no}}</ref>部队主要依赖于2003年美国入侵伊拉克时所缴获的伊拉克陆军的旧武器，那时佩什梅格武装很活跃。在此之前，一些武器也是在[[1991年伊拉克起义|1991年伊拉克起义]]期间缴获的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2013/06/iraq-asks-krg-for-pre-saddam-weapons.html#|title=Iraqi Defense Ministry Asks KRG To Return Saddam-Era Weapons - Al-Monitor: the Pulse of the Middle East|work=Al-Monitor|accessdate=20 March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115214454/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2013/06/iraq-asks-krg-for-pre-saddam-weapons.html|archivedate=2015年1月15日|df=}}</ref>在2014年6月ISIS发起进攻后，新伊拉克陆军撤退之际，佩什梅格武装据称再次设法得到了一些伊拉克陆军遗留的武器。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thenational.ae/world/middle-east/as-isil-retreats-iraqi-kurds-gain-new-ammunition#page1|title=As ISIL retreats, Iraqi Kurds gain new ammunition|author=Hugh Naylor|publisher=|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2016-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160418234620/http://www.thenational.ae/world/middle-east/as-isil-retreats-iraqi-kurds-gain-new-ammunition#page1|dead-url=no}}</ref>自2014年8月以来，佩什梅格武装还缴获了一些来自ISIS的武器。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/03/kurdish-forces-captured-a-isis-base-after-a-two-day-siege-but-the-isis-fighters-inside-somehow-slipped-away/|title=Kurdish forces captured an ISIS base after a two-day siege — but the ISIS fighters inside somehow slipped away|author=Richard Spencer, The Telegraph|date=3 October 2014|work=National Post|accessdate=20 March 2015}}</ref>

2014年8月ISIS进攻后，多个政府决定使用诸如轻型武器、夜视仪和弹药的轻武器装备来装备佩什梅格部队。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/aug/14/uk-britain-arms-supply-kurdish-forces-iraq-isis|title=UK prepares to supply arms directly to Kurdish forces fighting Isis|author=Nicholas Watt|work=the Guardian|accessdate=23 October 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003318/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/aug/14/uk-britain-arms-supply-kurdish-forces-iraq-isis|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ekurd.net/mismas/articles/misc2014/8/state8392.htm|title=Seven western states join US to arm Iraqi Kurdistan: Pentagon|publisher=|accessdate=23 October 2014|archive-date=2020-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200618065646/https://ekurd.net/mismas/articles/misc2014/8/state8392.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/aug/11/us-arm-peshmerga-iraq-kurdistan-isis|title=US to directly arm Kurdish peshmerga forces in bid to thwart Isis offensive|author=Spencer Ackerman|work=the Guardian|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015730/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/aug/11/us-arm-peshmerga-iraq-kurdistan-isis|dead-url=no}}</ref>但库尔德官员和佩什梅格都强调，他们没有得到足够的装备。他们同时强调，巴格达甚至阻止轻型武器流入库尔德地区，武器需要直接发往库尔德地区政府而不是通过巴格达。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/nov/21/iraqi-kurds-us-we-need-heavy-weapons-defeat-islami/|title=Iraqi Kurds to U.S.: We need heavy weapons to defeat Islamic State|work=The Washingtion Times|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2020-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200414053424/https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/nov/21/iraqi-kurds-us-we-need-heavy-weapons-defeat-islami/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/iraqs-kurds-appeal-for-new-us-arms-to-combat-islamic-state/2014/11/12/d2a0fe28-6aa6-11e4-9fb4-a622dae742a2_story.html|title=Iraq’s Kurds